OL,3,CThames Water sinks to #1.6bn loss as
OL,4,Cdebt mountain balloons
OL,6,FTroubled Thames Water has revealed it
OL,7,Fslumped to a #1.65 billion annual loss
OL,8,Fand saw its debt mountain balloon to
OL,9,F#16.79 billion.
OL,11,FThe struggling utility tumbled to the
OL,12,Fpre-tax loss in the year to March 31
OL,13,Ffrom profits of #157 million the
OL,14,Fprevious year after it booked a #1.27
OL,15,Fbillion bad debt provision on
OL,16,Fintercompany loans and set aside #122
OL,17,Fmillion for fines from Ofwat, among
OL,18,Fother costs.
