OL,3,CThames Water sinks to #1.6bn loss as
OL,4,Cdebt mountain balloons
OL,6,FThe group's full year results showed
OL,7,Fits mammoth net debts swelled by
OL,8,Fanother #1.65 billion over the year,
OL,9,Fwhile it revealed a "disappointing"
OL,10,Fperformance on pollution and sewage
OL,11,Fspills.
OL,13,FThe figures come as the water firm
OL,14,Fremains in talks over a rescue funding
OL,15,Fdeal with senior creditors after
OL,16,Fprivate equity firm KKR last month
OL,17,Fpulled out of plans to inject much-
OL,18,Fneeded cash.
