OL,3,CThames Water sinks to #1.6bn loss as
OL,4,Cdebt mountain balloons
OL,6,FChris Weston, chief executive of
OL,7,FThames Water, said: "We recognise that
OL,8,Four current gearing is too high and,
OL,9,Fto address this, we are progressing
OL,10,Fwith our Senior Creditors' plan to
OL,11,Frecapitalise the business which will
OL,12,Fsee us return to a more stable
OL,13,Ffinancial foundation.
OL,15,F"This will come with a requirement to
OL,16,Freset the regulatory landscape and
OL,17,Facknowledge it will take at least a
OL,18,Fdecade to turn Thames around."
